---
import Base from '../layouts/Base.astro';
import Nav from '../components/Nav.astro';
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';
---

<Base title="Privacy Policy" description="AIR Lab privacy policy — how we collect, use, and protect your information.">
  <Nav slot="nav" />

  <div class="page-hero" style="padding-bottom: 60px;">
    <div class="page-hero-content">
      <div class="section-label">Legal</div>
      <h1>Privacy <strong>Policy</strong></h1>
    </div>
  </div>

  <section style="background: #fff;">
    <div style="max-width: 760px; font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.8; color: var(--muted); font-weight: 300;">
      <p style="margin-bottom: 32px;">AIR Lab is committed to protecting your privacy. This Privacy Policy explains how we collect, use, and safeguard information when you visit airlab.aero.</p>

      <h3 style="font-size: 18px; font-weight: 600; color: var(--navy); margin-bottom: 12px; margin-top: 40px;">1. Information We Collect</h3>
      <p>We may collect information you provide directly to us, such as when you submit our contact form (name, email address, organisation, and message). We also collect standard analytics data such as pages visited, time spent on pages, and browser type via anonymised analytics tools.</p>

      <h3 style="font-size: 18px; font-weight: 600; color: var(--navy); margin-bottom: 12px; margin-top: 40px;">2. How We Use Information</h3>
      <p>Information collected through our contact form is used solely to respond to your enquiry. We do not sell, trade, or otherwise transfer your personal information to third parties without your consent, except as required by law.</p>

      <h3 style="font-size: 18px; font-weight: 600; color: var(--navy); margin-bottom: 12px; margin-top: 40px;">3. Cookies</h3>
      <p>This website may use cookies to enhance your browsing experience. You can choose to disable cookies through your browser settings. Disabling cookies may affect the functionality of some parts of this website.</p>

      <h3 style="font-size: 18px; font-weight: 600; color: var(--navy); margin-bottom: 12px; margin-top: 40px;">4. Data Security</h3>
      <p>We implement appropriate technical and organisational measures to protect your personal information against unauthorised access, alteration, disclosure, or destruction.</p>

      <h3 style="font-size: 18px; font-weight: 600; color: var(--navy); margin-bottom: 12px; margin-top: 40px;">5. Third-Party Services</h3>
      <p>Our website uses Sanity as a content management system and Netlify for hosting. These services may process data in accordance with their own privacy policies. We encourage you to review their policies.</p>

      <h3 style="font-size: 18px; font-weight: 600; color: var(--navy); margin-bottom: 12px; margin-top: 40px;">6. Your Rights</h3>
      <p>You have the right to access, correct, or request deletion of personal information we hold about you. To exercise these rights, please contact us via the <a href="/contact" style="color: var(--teal); text-decoration: none;">contact form</a>.</p>

      <h3 style="font-size: 18px; font-weight: 600; color: var(--navy); margin-bottom: 12px; margin-top: 40px;">7. Changes to This Policy</h3>
      <p>We may update this Privacy Policy from time to time. Changes will be posted on this page with an updated date. Continued use of this website constitutes acceptance of any changes.</p>

      <p style="margin-top: 48px; font-size: 14px; color: rgba(11,26,47,0.4);">Last updated: April 2026</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <Footer slot="footer" />
</Base>
